{"tid":994912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"<女權閪又贏>以花比喻女性被批性別歧視 鄭雨盛發文道歉","createTime":"2019-01-25T05:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T11:40:15.000Z","uid":109136,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"bed155ed90d65e1adb34838023cc18b24ba3f902","tid":994912,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:03:46.000Z","msg":"以韓國女星廉晶雅、李泰蘭、尹世雅、吳娜拉、金瑞亨主演的韓國《天空城堡》(Sky Castle)，現正熱播。45歲型男韓星鄭雨盛日前受訪時，以花比喻同門女星廉晶雅演技好：「她證明了花是不會凋謝的」。不過，廉晶雅對其讚美另有看法，她指以花比喻女演員，是物化女性，有性別歧視之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n鄭雨盛今日於IG上就事件道歉，稱自己無性別歧視意圖：「不過若我的表達方式令大家感到不便，在此向大家道歉。透過今次爭議，令我思考中原來我們平時的用語，會無意中涉及歧視，之後會好好反省，並注意用語，同時感謝大家指摘及教訓。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190124/_2019012415112513267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190124%2F_2019012415112513267.jpg&h=b0e9775c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭雨盛(左)、廉晶雅(右)。"},{"pid":"a6357a5236dea80d3e3424003eaf3dda5e9e6124","tid":994912,"uid":69098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676eccd534b7141067f9af14c7c6616284cf44ff","tid":994912,"uid":109136,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"a6357a5236dea80d3e3424003eaf3dda5e9e6124","tid":994912,"uid":69098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" c